textBeforeTable: Scoring Summary Facebook Photo Feature From the Game     The #1 vs #2 Private School matchup between the past two state champions lived up to all the advance billing. Liberty Christian Academy, the defending D1 VISAA State champions, held on to defeat Fork Union Military Academy 36-33. The outcome wasn't decided until the finals seconds when a 45-yard field goal attempt by Dylan McCormick was short. Liberty Christian Academy 36 Fork Union 33 October 12, 2012 Liberty Christian wins #1 vs #2 showdown Will Garlick VirginiaPreps.com Senior Writer Rivals Fan Shop
